This patch changes the .desktop file (provided by Debian's package) so that it
reports the right version of the .desktop specification and uses the name of
the icon without the extension (so without specifying the format) to allow
other themes to replace it with icons in other formats (such as svg).
It also remove GNOME from the categories as VLC is desktop-agnostic.
Index: vlc-0.8.4/debian/vlc.desktop
===================================================================
